data.description: **MOVE-IN READY!!** Welcome to 34717 Pinehurst Greene Way in the desirable golf community of Lake Bernadette! NEW ROOF IN 2023! This welcoming 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home also features an office/den, and a lanai with vinyl sliding windows that is heated and cooled (but not counted in the living area sq/footage). As you approach the property, lush and vibrant landscaping welcomes you to your own little slice of heaven! Inside, you'll find a great split floorplan layout, and no carpet! The kitchen has been tastefully upgraded with stainless steel appliances and granite counters. All appliances are 5 years old or newer. The kitchen also features a closet pantry, breakfast nook, and access to the laundry room and garage (the garage is a spacious 2 car garage). You're going to love the spacious primary bedroom with high ceilings and en-suite bathroom. The bathroom features both a garden tub and shower as well as dual vanities and a makeup desk. The large office/den also connects to the primary bathroom for quick access. The family room offers great space for entertaining, and also gives access to the lanai. The lanai features an electric fireplace, as well as a portable window a/c unit. The windows on the lanai are sliding vinyl over screen...the perfect hang-out spot to sip your coffee and watch the golfers duff around! Speaking of golf, your soon-to-be new home is located on the 12th hole of the Links of Lake Bernadette. LLB is an 18 hole championship golf course that is open to the public at a reasonable rate, and also offers memberships. The annual Lake Bernadette CDD fee is EXTREMELY reasonable and affords you access to all of the community amenities (private/gated access to 2 swimming pools, tennis/pickle ball courts, basketball courts, playground and more). Very golf cart friendly community (check with golf course for outside cart usage rules). Call today to schedule your private tour!
